features: Complete Package for DIY Enthusiasts: our kit contains 1 wedding brooms for jumping, 2 rolls of ribbons, 100 pearls in a pack, 2 eucalyptus leaves, 14 artificial roses (small and large), and 1 delphinium, these elements can be arranged as desired, letting you add and DIY a personal touch to the broom, please note that you will need to bring your own hot glue gun and scissors for assembly

Elegant Color Combination: this wedding broom mainly features a tasteful natural colors; Whether it's the milky ribbon tied around the broom, or the blend of milky white and white flowers decorating it, we've ensured to maintain a soft and romantic color palette that resonates with the ceremony occasion, jump over the broom and embrace your happiness

Attention to the Small Details: our wedding decorative broom has meticulous attention to detail, the kit includes pearls that are about 5 mm in diameter and miniature roses that measure about 1.57 x 1.57 inches; These small additions to the broom are intricately placed to enhance the overall appearance, making it even more attractive and elegant

Quality Natural Material: embrace a spiritual and antique African American mores at your wedding with our wedding broom for jumping decorated; Mainly crafted from natural grass, this broom represents benediction and wish, the natural colored broom at a size of approximately 11.81 x 25.2 inches is a symbol of sweeping away negative energy and welcoming positivity

Multi Functional Wedding Accessory: more than just a jumping broom, this wedding broom for jumping the broom ceremony functions well as house cleaning brooms and can also be applied as decorations for holidays; This versatile property sets it apart from regular wedding accessories, giving you a charming atmosphere for your wedding and activities
body.description: Features: If you're hoping to give something attractive and thoughtful, this wedding DIY whisk broom is a nice choice. A handmade gift like this, packed with history and tradition, is going to be appreciated. Its aesthetically appealing look adds up to its distinctiveness. Our African American wedding broom isn't just stylish, it's also thoughtfully sized, it is comfortable and convenient for couples to jump during the ceremony. This makes the jumping tradition easy and fun, contributing to the unforgettable moments of your big day.
